License: MIT
Description: # pylic - A Python license checker
        
        Reads the pyproject.toml file and checks all installed licenses recursively.
        
        ## Example Configuration
        
        ```pyproject.toml
        [tool.pylic]
        allowed_licenses = [
            'MIT',
            'BSD'
        ]
        whitelisted_packages = [
            "examplePyPackage"
        ]
        ```
        
        ## Development
        
        Required tools:
        - GitHub cli (https://github.com/cli/cli)
        
